<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ zhī dào, zhǔ zhī dào, yī qiè zhǔ dōu zhī dào. nǐ wèi tā zuò duō zuò shǎo, zhǔ dōu zhī dào.
 shì miǎn qiáng shì gān xīn, zhǔ dōu zhī dào. zǒng yào yǐ qiān bēi shù yāo, yīn zhǔ dōu zhī dào.
 zhǔ bì jiān gù wǒ men de xīn, yīn tā zhī dào wǒ men de xū yào.
 zǒng yào fú zài shén dà néng de quán xià, zhǔ dōu zhī dào, zhǔ dōu zhī dào.</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ zhī dào 迦南988</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
